ZH: 我在海滩上戴着一顶草帽。
EN: I wore a straw hat at the beach.

ZH: 他戴着一顶透气的草帽避免中暑。
EN: He wore a breathable straw hat to prevent heatstroke.

ZH: 她用彩色布条装饰了自己的草帽。
EN: She decorated her straw hat with colorful ribbons.

ZH: 公园里有个小卖部卖着各种样式的草帽。
EN: There is a kiosk in the park selling straw hats in different styles.

ZH: 她把一块牛仔布系在草帽上，使它看起来更时尚。
EN: She tied a piece of denim fabric around her straw hat to make it look more fashionable.

ZH: 在热带地区，人们常戴草帽来防晒。
EN: People often wear straw hats to protect themselves from the sun in tropical regions.

ZH: 这顶草帽是我在乡村购物中心买的。
EN: I bought this straw hat at the countryside shopping center.

ZH: 孩子们在河边玩耍，带着草帽。
EN: The children were playing by the river, wearing straw hats.

ZH: 她用亮闪闪的珠子给草帽增添了一些颜色。
EN: She added some color to the straw hat with shiny beads.

ZH: 这中草帽完全透气，非常轻便。
EN: This straw hat is completely breathable and very lightweight.

ZH: 我的爷爷戴着一顶旧草帽，总是很随和。
EN: My grandpa always wears an old straw hat and has a relaxed demeanor.

ZH: 他戴着一顶紫色的草帽，非常吸引眼球。
EN: He wore a purple straw hat that caught everyone's attention.

ZH: 她认为草帽是夏天必备的配饰。
EN: She thinks straw hats are essential accessories for summer.

ZH: 阳光下，她戴着一顶草帽在泳池旁边晒太阳。
EN: Under the sun, she wore a straw hat and sunbathed by the pool.

ZH: 这顶草帽非常耐用，我已经用了好几年了。
EN: This straw hat is very durable; I have been using it for several years.

ZH: 他们在农场里采摘蔬菜，头上戴着草帽防晒。
EN: They were picking vegetables in the farm, wearing straw hats to protect themselves from the sun.

ZH: 喂，不要忘记带上你的草帽，我们要去海滩了！
EN: Hey, don't forget to bring your straw hat, we're going to the beach!

ZH: 这位妇女用细绳将草帽牢牢地系在头上，不怕风吹走。
EN: The woman securely fastened the straw hat to her head with a thin rope, not afraid of it being blown away by the wind.

ZH: 这条草帽是由稻草编制而成的。
EN: This straw hat is made from woven straw.

ZH: 他用草帽遮住阳光，仔细刻画着沙滩上的景色。
EN: He used a straw hat to shield the sun and carefully depicted the scenery on the beach.
